content.summary: A candidate seeking a role in a company that encourages professional growth, with a focus on utilizing knowledge and skills. Possesses good presentation skills, adaptability, creativity, leadership abilities, and proficiency in Python, SQL, MS-Excel, Anaplan, Core Java, and more. Holds certifications from The Functional Programming Language (Python), Finance for Non-Financial Professionals, SQL-Basic and intermediate, MS-EXCEL-Basic and Intermediate, Anaplan Level 1 Model Building, Anaplan Level 2 Model Building, TCR innovation, and Walkover University. Graduated with a B.Tech in CSE from Medi-caps University Indore (2019-2023) and completed 12th CBSE from Shri Agrasen Vidyalaya Indore with 58% (2018-2019) and 10th CBSE from Allegiance Academy KUKSHI with an 8.2 CGPA (2016-2017). Attended a 3-month course in mathematics from CUEMATH and served as an HR Intern at MyDigitalShelf for 3 months.
